{{Infobox person | honorific_prefix = | name = Erol Özensoy | honorific_suffix = | image = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{birth year and age|1953}} | birth_place = [[İskenderun]], [[Hatay Province|Hatay]], Turkey | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | resting_place = | resting_place_coordinates = | monuments = | residence = | nationality = Turkish | other_names = | ethnicity = | citizenship = | education = [[Chemical Engineer]], [[Metallurgical Engineer]], [[Chemist]] | alma_mater = [[Imperial College London]], [[Colorado School of Mines]], [[Ankara University]] | occupation = | years_active = | employer = | organization = [[Kimetsan]] | agent = | known_for = | notable_works = | style = | influences = | influenced = | home_town = | salary = | net_worth = | height = | weight = | television = | title = | term = | predecessor = | successor = | party = | movement = | opponents = | boards = | religion = | denomination = | criminal_charge = | criminal_penalty = | criminal_status = | spouse = Hatice Ozensoy | partner = | children = Elvin Merve Ozensoy, [[Erdem Duhan Özensoy]] | parents = | relatives = | callsign = | awards = | signature = | signature_alt = | signature_size = | module = | website = | footnotes = | box_width = }} '''Erol Ozensoy''' (born 1953), a self-made [[Turkish people|Turkish]] [[entrepreneur]], [[industrialist]] and businessmen, who founded [[Kimetsan]], one of the largest chemical companies in Turkey today.
==Biography== Ozensoy was born 1953 in [[Hatay Province|Hatay]], [[Turkey]]. He was educated in [[chemical engineering]] and [[chemistry]], at the [[Ankara University]]. After having his master of science degree in Turkey, he won the scholarship of Turkish Government and studied [[metallurgical engineering]] at the [[Colorado School of Mines]]. After completing his second master's degree, he got his Ph.D. at the [[Imperial College London]] in hydrometallurgy. He then returned home to teach at [[Middle East Technical University]] and after 1986, he founded [[Kimetsan]] company. Currently, Ozensoy is the chairman of Kimetsan. He is married to Hatice, and he has 2 children Elvin Merve Ozensoy and [[Erdem Duhan Özensoy]].
